def mean_intersection_area(first: gpd.GeoDataFrame, second: gpd.GeoDataFrame) -> float:
    """Calculate the mean intersection ratio of polygons. Both arguments are geodataframes."""
    # Calculate the intersection
    intersection = first.intersection(second)

    # Calculate the area of the intersection
    intersection_area = intersection.area.sum()

    # Calculate the area of the union
    union_area = first.area.sum() + second.area.sum() - intersection_area

    # Calculate the mean intersection ratio
    return intersection_area / union_area
